---
description: Life Harness project-root guardrails and canonical agent entry
alwaysApply: true
---

## Canonical agent entry
- Run `npm run agent:preflight` first.
- Do not treat `agent:bootstrap` as the canonical entrypoint.
## Bootstrap compatibility
- Keep `npm run agent:bootstrap` as a backwards-compatible/internal helper.
- If you need the old bootstrap-style repo orientation, use `npm run agent:preflight -- --bootstrap`.
## Guardrails / boundaries
- Keep `src/core` UI-independent.
- `app/` and `src/` must not import from `services/`.
- Raw Lab runtime must not import board state/actions/provider/persistence.
- Ask Harness runtime must not import Raw Lab personality/thread internals.
## Cheap checks
- `npm run check:agent-budget`
- `npm run check:boundaries`
